  "text": "However, before the deployment of these Web pages in WebCIS, we needed a technique to evaluate them, particularly to ensure that we presented the information needs solutions in a manner that was acceptable to the typical user of WebCIS. Though there are a number of usability techniques available (e.g., verbal protocol analysis [CITATION_1] , cognitive task analysis [CITATION_2] , cognitive walkthrough [CITATION_3] , Minor usability problem: fixing this should be given low priority 3",
